data.description: Welcome Home Friends!!! Take a look at this BEAUTIFUL MOVE IN READY 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home which boasts 2,248 sq ft of living space with a spacious 3 car garage. This open concept floor plan is highly sought after and is perfect for entertaining guests! Georgeous eat in kitchen, formal dining, and huge family room, makes it perfect for a growing family. A separate bedroom and full bath, separate from the master and other bedrooms, would be perfect for a mother in law suite. Porcelain tile in the living space as well as carpet in the bedrooms, make it easy to keep clean. The backyard features Bluetooth Surround Sound, Built in Fire Pit, a grass area perfect for a playground, as well as a huge covered patio. This home has Security System with Cameras and will not last long at this price!
